WEBVTT

00:00:00.580 --> 00:00:03.698
This is Scabbers.
Pathetic, isn't he?

00:00:03.915 --> 00:00:05.078
A little.

00:00:05.292 --> 00:00:08.626
Fred gave me a spell
to turn him yellow. Want to see?

00:00:08.837 --> 00:00:10.876
Yeah.

00:00:17.637 --> 00:00:19.262
Has anyone seen a toad?

00:00:19.639 --> 00:00:22.308
- A boy named Neville's lost one.
- No.

00:00:22.893 --> 00:00:27.221
Oh, are you doing magic?
Let's see, then.

